column5: great report & pics !!! too bad about the broken rod,but it worked out nice anyways,great looking creek too,nice scenery...
Thanx for the report.  Awesome pix!  What's up with this underline Thingy??  Can't get rid of it
great report - and some rul purty browns.
Some very nice fish Thanks for the report
Loved it dooood!  Great report and pics.  Great escape for you and your buddy.  Thanks for posting that up!
What a great looking creek! Impressive pics too. Thanks for sharing your trip with us.
Nice report with beautiful pics... thx for sharing.
Great pictures, really describes what it is like where you were - just beautiful!  That sucks about the rod tho, but it didn't stop you guys from fishing and catching
Everything my opening days would be in a perfect world Dave, less the broken rod of course. Thanks for sharing, I'm still gaga over the stream, trying to recall if I waded it myself decades back.
Nice adorable pretty funky creek with beer and browns pricessless
Was definitely a good opener folks.  Was up again in the same area last weekend and did just as well if not better.
